      "description": "Ubud — the inland spiritual and wellness hub of Bali, nestled among rice terraces and river valleys. A global convergence point for yoga, cacao ceremony, sound healing, ecstatic dance, breathwork, bhakti music, and plant medicine traditions — held by temples and studios woven through the town and its surrounding villages.",
