      "id": "practice:peace-bathing",
      "type": "practice",
      "name": "Peace Bathing",
      "description": "Peace Bathing — monthly online group channeled healing sessions held by Anne Tucker, where the Angels raise vibration into the soothing realm of peace, adapting to current Earth energies. A practice the user was already holding before finding Anne; joining the sessions deepened it.",
      "properties": {
        "claimed": false,
